
You need to install:

1.Visual Studio Code: https://visualstudio.microsoft.com/

2.MiKTeX: https://miktex.org/download 
  Precautions: During the installation select the followings options for prevent
  later conflicts.
  
  1.Install MikTeX for anyone who uses this computer (all users)
  2.Install MiKTeX to: Installation path by default
  3.Preferred paper: Letter 
    Install missing packages on-the-fly: Yes
  4.Start installation
  5.Selection: Check for updates now
  6.Finish 
   
3.Strawberry Perl: https://strawberryperl.com/ 

4.In Visual Studio Code install the followings extensions:
- LaTex
- LaTex Workshop
- LaTex Language Support
- LaTex Utilities